## T-001 Implementation Summary

**Subtask**: Design and generate Autoresearch custom app icon set

### What was done

1. **Designed a custom SVG icon** (`autoresearch-icon.svg`) featuring:
   - Blue-to-indigo gradient rounded rectangle background (AI/tech theme)
   - Magnifying glass with integrated "A" letter (research/autoresearch)
   - Gear at the handle end (automation)
   - Subtle circuit-node decorative elements (tech feel)

2. **Generated all icon formats** using `pnpm tauri icon` from the 1024x1024 source:
   - **15 PNG files**: 32x32, 64x64, 128x128, 128x128@2x, icon.png (1024x1024), plus 10 Square*/StoreLogo Windows tiles
   - **icon.icns**: macOS icon with 10 resolutions (16x16 through 512x512@2x)
   - **icon.ico**: Windows icon with 6 resolutions (16x16 through 256x256)

3. **Verified acceptance criteria**:
   - All 16 original icon files replaced (not Tauri defaults — icon.png went from 14KB to 211KB)
   - icon.png is 1024x1024 (requirement met)
   - Visual consistency across sizes — all derived from single SVG source
   - icns/ico contain complete multi-size icon sets

